From cou.: 12 Pharmaceutical products analyzed were: Aspirina®+C (Bayer S.A.), Melhoral®C (DM Indústria Farmacêutica LTDA), Doril® (DM Indústria Farmacêutica LTDA) and Sandoz® (Novartis Biociências S.A.). The first two pharmaceutical products contained the two analytes as active compounds and other possibly excipient interferences. Doril® contains ASA and caffeine as active compounds, while Sandoz® presents just AA as active compound and possible excipient interferences.
From Soup: 12 Pharmaceutical products analyzed were: Aspirina ® +C (Bayer S.A.), Melhoral ® C (DM Indústria Farmacêutica LTDA), Doril ® (DM Indústria Farmacêutica LTDA) and Sandoz ® (Novartis Biociências S.A.). The first two pharmaceutical products contained the two analytes as active compounds and other possibly excipient interferences. Doril ® contains ASA and caffeine as active compounds, while Sandoz ® presents just AA as active compound and possible excipient interferences.
