From cou.: 14 Reference methods used for validation of the MCR-ALS determinations of ASA and AA by FIA were performed by HPLC and iodimetric titration, respectively. The sample preparation was the same as described in the previous section and the determinations were performed in triplicate (for each pharmaceutical product).
From Soup: 14 Reference methods used for validation of the MCR-ALS determinations of ASA and AA by FIA were performed by HPLC and iodimetric titration , respectively. The sample preparation was the same as described in the previous section and the determinations were performed in triplicate (for each pharmaceutical product).
